{"tid":2352032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大連疫情出現超級傳播者令33人染疫","createTime":"2021-01-03T17:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T23:10:39.000Z","uid":344793,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6797ebc38ed10ef929396ea9423a8eaed579d8c5","tid":2352032,"uid":344793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"遼寧省大連市出現新型冠狀病毒疫情，78人受感染，包括29男49女，年齢由3個月至88歲。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現有一名超級傳播者，造成33人染疫。 巿衛健委人員在記者會指，今次疫情傳播速度快、涉及地點多及傳播力強。初步判定<span class=\"blue\">疫情源於受病毒污染的進口冷藏產品</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，感染碼頭搬運工人，再通過聚餐及搬屋活動，傳到一個小區、一座商業大廈及大連醫科大學附屬門診。其中同一名商廈業主有關的確診病例及無症狀感染者共有33人。至於同這座商廈有關的病例合共有65宗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2373260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2373260&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=7071a911\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2373260</a>"},{"pid":"4e2ed540f87693236452c768a96d337d00a3ff8a","tid":2352032,"uid":55913,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"繼續自欺欺人就o岩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd0c50d1f18d156314ab50799999b5128cb8fd9","tid":2352032,"uid":6030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"睇咗大埔，嚇一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65ac022c7bc7b628924271ab173771a905e1ff9","tid":2352032,"uid":368267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"爆到佢冚家剷就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa93bd0f7d498238ba61b79346fa48e7c1e95f71","tid":2352032,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"死亡人數萬年4634<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji